607
00:32:30,961 --> 00:32:33,160
This incident occurred two months ago.

608
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:36,281
A passerby recorded it
and posted it online.

609
00:32:36,481 --> 00:32:39,360
Wen Yong's wife is a teacher
at a key high school in our city.

610
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:41,880
It caused quite a stir
after she was recognized.

611
00:32:42,241 --> 00:32:45,521
Later, we heard Wen Yong's wife
had someone take down the video.

612
00:32:45,521 --> 00:32:46,560
to protect her job.

613
00:32:47,281 --> 00:32:49,840
If Wen Yong and his wife
had a strained relationship,

614
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:52,961
his wife could have benefited
from his disappearance.

615
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:54,800
Then why was she
so determined to find him?

616
00:32:55,441 --> 00:32:56,400
It's hard to say.

617
00:32:56,721 --> 00:33:00,001
Wen Yong's wife did have
a solid alibi at the time.

618
00:33:00,921 --> 00:33:04,880
And Jiang Xiaohua found the attacker
looked like Gao Liang's girlfriend.

619
00:33:05,281 --> 00:33:06,600
Pull up that sketch.

620
00:33:11,721 --> 00:33:15,201
So far, that fingerprint
has been found at four locations.

621
00:33:15,721 --> 00:33:17,281
Namely, the Cheng Jianmin case,

622
00:33:17,281 --> 00:33:18,320
the Zhou Lianqin case,

623
00:33:18,520 --> 00:33:20,376
the Wen Yong case,
and the Liu Xiaofeng case.

624
00:33:21,080 --> 00:33:23,160
The current evidence
on Cheng Jianmin's death

625
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,281
is insufficient to be classified
as a case.

626
00:33:26,320 --> 00:33:30,400
But there was testimony that Wen Yong
had been attacked at the scene.

627
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:32,961
The forensic unit's analysis

628
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,201
revealed that the marks
on the roof beam,

629
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:37,880
were likely not left
by Zhou Lianqin himself.

630
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:40,600
So the alleged suicide
has inconsistencies.

631
00:33:41,681 --> 00:33:45,360
While there's clearer evidence
that Liu Xiaofeng was murdered.

632
00:33:46,241 --> 00:33:48,080
In the Cheng Jianmin
and Zhou Lianqin cases,

633
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:52,001
the suspect at the scene
was an unidentified young male.

634
00:33:53,041 --> 00:33:54,721
But in the Wen Yong
and Liu Xiaofeng cases,

635
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:57,600
it was this unidentified young female.

636
00:33:57,921 --> 00:34:01,560
Now, we only know she's the girlfriend
of someone named Gao Liang.

637
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:05,600
Gao Liang's identity
remains unknown as well.

638
00:34:06,001 --> 00:34:08,600
He's also linked to that arson case
in the urban village.

639
00:34:09,640 --> 00:34:11,200
Through witness interrogations,

640
00:34:11,441 --> 00:34:13,361
we identified Gao Liang

641
00:34:13,361 --> 00:34:17,600
bears significant resemblance
to the suspect in the first two cases.

642
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:20,521
If we confirm it's the same person,

643
00:34:20,881 --> 00:34:21,961
we can state

644
00:34:22,521 --> 00:34:27,521
that this couple is central
to all these cases.

645
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:34,521
Assuming all these are connected cases,

646
00:34:35,160 --> 00:34:36,560
what's their motive?

647
00:34:38,521 --> 00:34:41,961
Ordinary crimes usually involve money,
relationships, or revenge.

648
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:44,640
But these victims

649
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:47,200
have no connections
in work or personal lives.

650
00:34:47,961 --> 00:34:51,881
It's unlikely for them to hold grudges
against so many simultaneously.

651
00:34:52,521 --> 00:34:54,600
So we can't rule out contract killings.

652
00:34:54,881 --> 00:34:55,881
Is this a TV drama plot?

653
00:34:56,041 --> 00:34:58,160
A criminal duo hiring hitmen?

654
00:35:00,441 --> 00:35:01,600
Hard to tell.

655
00:35:01,961 --> 00:35:04,760
The killers might not
be motivated by money,

656
00:35:04,881 --> 00:35:07,001
but by purposes unknown to us.

657
00:35:07,881 --> 00:35:09,481
Aside from Cheng Jianmin's case,

658
00:35:09,841 --> 00:35:13,600
the subsequent cases
share some common threads.

659
00:35:13,841 --> 00:35:15,321
Of course, this is just my analysis.

660
00:35:15,321 --> 00:35:16,521
It might not be accurate.

661
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,200
Zhou Lianqin,

662
00:35:19,001 --> 00:35:19,921
a debt-dodging deadbeat

663
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,560
who collected funds and vanished.

664
00:35:21,912 --> 00:35:23,736
Wen Yong,
domestic violence and prostitution.

665
00:35:24,321 --> 00:35:26,001
Liu Xiaofeng tortured
and killed animals,

666
00:35:26,001 --> 00:35:27,560
