755
00:38:53,041 --> 00:38:55,600
Could our suspect
be doing something similar?

756
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:57,640
We'll resume the Wen Yong case tomorrow.

757
00:38:58,680 --> 00:39:00,080
Hurry up and eat.

